'''Monika Pedersen''' (born 21 December 1978) is a [[Denmark|Danish]] singer of the band Sinphonia and former vocalist<ref>https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=777190648972950&&id=216255085066512</ref> of "The World State" and the [[Norwegian people|Norwegian]] [[gothic metal]] band [[Sirenia (band)|Sirenia]], replacing Henriette Bordvik. She also contributed guest vocals to [[Mercenary (band)|Mercenary]], [[Effektor]], [[Evil Masquerade]], [[Manticora]] and [[Ad Noctum]].<ref name=myspace/>

==Discography==

=== With The World State  ===
*Flier EP - 2013
*Traced through Dust and Time - TBA

=== With Sinphonia ===
*When the Tide Breaks - 2000
*The Divine Disharmony - 2002
*Silence (EP) - 2005

=== With Sirenia ===
*[[Nine Destinies and a Downfall]] - 2007

==== Singles ====
*[[My Mind's Eye (Sirenia song)|My Mind's Eye]]

==== Music videos====
*[[My Mind's Eye (Sirenia song)|My Mind's Eye]]
*The Other Side

=== Guest Appearances ===
*[[Mercenary (band)|Mercenary]] - [[11 Dreams]] (2004)
*[[Evil Masquerade]] - [[Theatrical Madness]] (2005)

